[[佐治亚理工学院|佐治亚理工学院]]建立于[[南北战争|南北战争]]后不久，有近150年的历史。一开始只是一座小的商业学校，后来逐渐演变为[[美国东南部|美国东南部]]最大的理工学院。1978年，[[佐治亚理工学院历史区域|佐治亚理工学院历史区域]]被列入[[國家史蹟名錄|國家史蹟名錄]]。

==建立==
[[Image:AtlantaDuringCivilWar.jpg|Atlanta during the Civil War (c. 1864)]]
建立佐治亚理工学院的想法始于重建时期的1865年。两位前[[美利坚联盟国|邦联]]官员{{Link-en|约翰·弗莱彻·汉森|John Fletcher Hanson}}和{{Link-en|纳撒尼尔·埃德温·哈里斯|Nathaniel Edwin Harris}}相信南方需要提高科技实力以与北方竞争，这种观念也反映了许多普通南方人的看法。但由于南方是由农业主导，一所理工学校就成为必须了。<ref name="Hopkins">{{cite web | title = The Hopkins Administration, 1888-1895 | work = "A Thousand Wheels are set in Motion": The Building of Georgia Tech at the Turn of the 20th Century, 1888-1908 | publisher = Georgia Institute of Technology | url = http://www.library.gatech.edu/gtbuildings/hopkins.htm | accessdate = 2006-12-30 | archive-date = 2016-03-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303171041/http://www.library.gatech.edu/gtbuildings/hopkins.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>

1882年，佐治亚州的精英授权哈里斯领导的[[佐治亚州立法院|佐治亚州立法院]]派团去美国东北考察，以学习理工学校如何运作。<ref name="NewSouthCreed">{{cite journal | last = Brittain | first = James E. | coauthors = Robert C. McMath, Jr. | title = Engineers and the New South Creed: The Formation and Early Development of Georgia Tech  | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_technology-and-culture_1977-04_18_2/page/175 | journal = Technology and Culture | volume = 18 | issue = 2 | pages = 175-201 | publisher = Johns Hopkins University Press | doi = 10.2307/3103955 |date=April 1977}}</ref>{{Link-en|帕特里克·怀斯·梅尔|Patrick Hues Mell}}，当时[[佐治亚大学|佐治亚大学]]的校长，坚持认为大学的主校区应选在Athens，作为农学部、工学部。尽管有梅尔反对，一所独立的学院还是建立起来了。<ref name="PatrickMell">{{cite web |last=Mell |first=P.H., Jr. |title=CHAPTER XIX. Efforts Towards Completing the Technological School as a Department of the University of Georgia |work=Life of Patrick Hues Mell |publisher=Baptist Book Concern |year=1895 |url=http://www.founders.org/library/mell_life/chap19.html |accessdate=2006-12-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20050407044425/http://www.founders.org/library/mell_life/chap19.html |archivedate=2005-04-07 }}</ref>创建时的校址位于当时亚特兰大北部边界（现在的城市已然扩展）。中央校区大山上的石碑显示该校第一座建筑的原址曾是内战中[[亚特兰大战役|亚特兰大战役]]中南军的堡垒。<ref name="CivilWarAtlanta">{{cite web | last = Lenz | first = Richard J. | title = Surrender Marker, Fort Hood, Change of Command Marker | work = The Civil War in Georgia, An Illustrated Travelers Guide | publisher = Sherpa Guides | url = http://sherpaguides.com/georgia/civil_war/atlanta/westview_area.html | accessdate = 2006-12-30 | date = November 2002 | archive-date = 2019-11-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191102014252/https://sherpaguides.com/georgia/civil_war/atlanta/westview_area.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>

==早期岁月==
